premise_source_doc_sentence: City of Evil is the third studio album by Avenged Sevenfold released on June 7 , 2005 by Warner Bros. .
Live in the LBC & Diamonds in the Rough is the first live DVD , and compilation album by heavy metal band Avenged Sevenfold released on September 16 , 2008 by Warner Bros. .
To date , Avenged Sevenfold has released seven studio albums , one live album/DVD , two compilation albums and eighteen singles and have sold over 8 million albums worldwide .

The album contains some of Avenged Sevenfold 's most popular and famous songs , including `` Bat Country '' , which is arguably their most successful to date , being one of their two singles certified Gold by the RIAA .

The discography of Avenged Sevenfold , an American heavy metal band , consists of seven studio albums , one soundtrack album , two compilation albums , 24 singles , two video albums and 20 music videos .
